name: Senior Thesis Visualizations
body:
### Analyzing Senior Theses

Past senior theses were obtained from the Tufts Digital Library archive. They were divided into subject (Biology, Psychology, Economics, English, and International Relations) and analyzed.

https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=${https://github.com/denalirao/thesis-Visualizations/blob/master/final%20visualizations.pdf}
